metadata.name: The Expolorer #1/10
metadata.description:
The Explorer

Lost in a galaxy light years away, There is a man searching for planets such as Earth.

This is the planet (0101077-Hothlithium) which is a snow like planet with some vegetation and some hope for the future.

See the year is 2077 Earth has become unstable for humanity to survive on, so thus started the exploration to look for other planets for the species to survive.

As the astronauts searched the galaxy's far and wide there have only been 3 planets that could sustain humans.

As they look deep into the outer bounds of space, Earth has turned into a war zone of anarchy, rebellion against those who try to rule with Technology.
